d |>
  distinct(unit, year, sold, level, bath) |>
  ggplot() + 
  aes(label = unit,
      x = year,
      #y = `net value`,
      y = sold,
      color = level) +
    geom_point() +
  geom_point(alpha = .5, aes(size = bath)) +
  geom_text_repel() +
  labs(title = "Comps for Touchstone #26",
